30/* Output per-alloc_pool memory usage statistics. */
31void
32dump_alloc_pool_statistics (void)
33{
34 if (! GATHER_STATISTICS)
35 return;
36
37 pool_allocator_usage.dump (ALLOC_POOL_ORIGIN);
38}
